Revision history for Linux::Inotify2::WatchDir::Simple

0.01    2025-11-08
        - Initial CPAN release
        - Simple polling-based filesystem monitoring
        - YAML and JSON configuration support
        - Multiple watchlist capability
        - Event filtering with regex patterns
        - Multiple action types: email, syslog, console, command
        - Recursive directory monitoring
        - Signal handling (SIGHUP reload, SIGTERM/SIGINT shutdown)
        - Daemon mode with PID file management
        - systemd integration with template service file
        - Log::Log4perl integration for structured logging
        - Email::Sender for flexible email delivery
        - Comprehensive POD documentation
        - Example configurations included
        - Test suite for core functionality

